                <h1>Band of misfits for Duke men&#039;s basketball develops into productive bench</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/837fd876-86eb-46c8-b317-7f2e72b7937d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;After&#x20;being&#x20;relegated&#x20;to&#x20;the&#x20;bench,&#x20;Trevon&#x20;Duval&#x20;has&#x20;made&#x20;the&#x20;most&#x20;of&#x20;his&#x20;new&#x20;role&#x20;and&#x20;dished&#x20;out&#x20;six&#x20;assists&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;second&#x20;half&#x20;of&#x20;Duke&#x2019;s&#x20;comeback&#x20;win&#x20;Saturday.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>After being relegated to the bench, Trevon Duval has made the most of his new role and dished out six assists in the second half of Duke’s comeback win Saturday.</p>

