                                                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="mailto:?subject=Band%20of%20misfits%20for%20Duke%20men%27s%20basketball%20develops%20into%20productive%20bench%20|%20The%20Chronicle&amp;message=Check%20out%20this%20article%20from%20The%20Chronicle%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukechronicle.com%2Farticle%2F2018%2F03%2Fband-of-misfits-for-duke-mens-basketball-develops-into-productive-bench" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="email" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></a></li>
